video.title: Masha and the Bear
video.synopsis: Lively little Masha lives near the forest, where she has wonderful adventures with her best friend — a bear who used to be in the circus.

episodes.synopsis: An unexpected visitor shakes things up in the forest; Masha flies to China to celebrate the New Year; Bear becomes a dashing Spaniard for the day.
episodes.title: No Work All Carnival / Happy New Year … Again! / Spanish Tunes

episodes.synopsis: French fashion inspires Masha to become a designer; A fluffy new friend from England gets lost in the forest; Masha sings from her heart about Italy.
episodes.title: Pink of Fashion / From England with Love / Where All Love to Sing

episodes.synopsis: Masha thinks big to fix her broken robot; Icy-cold weather drives Masha and Bear to sunny Mexico; Bear rubs a lamp and awakens a genie.
episodes.title: The Secret of Mashuko / When Cacti Bloom / Tales from the East

episodes.synopsis: Masha trades piano lessons for something better; Wild West fun comes to the forest; Masha returns a masterpiece to the museum; Masha sings about India.
episodes.title: Das ist gut! / Once in the Wild West / Almost Ancient Greek Story / The Magic Flute

episodes.synopsis: A phone call lifts Bear's spirits; Masha uses her imagination to create her own fairy tale; Masha interrupts Bear's sleep.
episodes.title: Coming Back Ain't Easy / The Very Fairy Tale / Rock-a-Bye, Baby!

episodes.synopsis: The wolves disguise their vehicle in hopes of nabbing some grub; Bear gets a hungry new housemate; The forest residents catch a glimpse of a ghost.
episodes.title: Driving Lessons / Like Cat and Mouse / A Ghost Story

episodes.synopsis: The wolves set out to rob a poultry farm; Masha joins Bear on his artistic hike through nature; Bear has a run-in with a stubborn bee.
episodes.title: Surprise! Surprise! / Liar, Liar, Pants on Fire! / The Three Mashketeers

episodes.synopsis: Masha receives an unexpected birthday gift; Bear can't tear himself away from his computer games; Masha is greeted by Christmas ghosts.
episodes.title: At Your Service / Game Over / A Christmas Carol

episodes.synopsis: Bear builds a rocket to send Masha and Panda to the moon; Masha and her friends put on a show; Masha gets to be queen for a day.
episodes.title: Twinkle, Twinkle, Little Star / All the World's a Stage / God Save the Queen!

episodes.synopsis: Masha comes down with a cold; Bear's friends stop by to play pool; A UFO lands in the woods; Bear makes music with a string quartet.
episodes.title: Best Medicine / That's Your Cue! / We Come in Peace! / Quartet Plus

episodes.synopsis: Rosie trades places with the wolves; Bear goes on a fishing trip; Masha finds a camera in Bear's closet; Masha runs off with a troupe of monkeys.
episodes.title: New Kids on the Block! / Fishy Story / Just Shoot Me / Monkey Business

episodes.synopsis: Masha and Panda go golfing with Bear; Bear preps for a trip around the world; Masha wants to play hockey; Bear helps Masha pick a career path.
episodes.title: Tee for Three / Around the World in One Day / What a Wonderful Game / Who Am I?

episodes.synopsis: Masha's painting project gets out of control; Masha and the hare play hockey; Bear tries to make a potion that will help him impress the female bear.
episodes.title: Picture Perfect / Swept Away / Growing Potion

episodes.synopsis: Bear makes over his home for the female bear; all the animals flee from Masha's attempts to help them; Bear and Masha set out on a journey together.
episodes.title: La Dolce Vita / Kidding Around / Bon Voyage

episodes.synopsis: Bear's birthday party gives Masha an idea; an accident causes Bear to start acting like Masha; Bear gets upset when the penguin only plays with Masha.
episodes.title: Once Upon a Year / Trading Places Day / All in the Family

episodes.synopsis: Bear gets a lesson in taking things easy; Masha discovers that Bear's magic hat can make her invisible; Masha introduces her cousin Dasha to Bear.
episodes.title: Terrible Power / Hat Trick / Two Much

episodes.synopsis: Bear and Masha try to shoot a movie; Bear plays in a tennis tournament; Masha wants to solve a puzzling crime like Sherlock Holmes.
episodes.title: And Action! / Victory Cry / The Puzzling Case

episodes.synopsis: Bear hires a nanny to watch Masha and Panda; Masha helps Bear and Panda make dumplings; Masha brings her own special magic to a costume ball.
episodes.title: Home-Grown Ninjas / Bon Appétit / Variety Show

episodes.synopsis: To everyone's surprise, Masha becomes a hero; Masha stirs up more trouble after watching a scary movie; Masha and Panda try to out-dance each other.
episodes.title: Self-Made Hero / The Thriller Night / Dance Fever

episodes.synopsis: Bear tries to build a time machine to visit his ancestors; Masha helps Bear plan a costume ball to cheer up the female bear; Masha starts to grow up.
episodes.title: Sabre-Toothed Bear / Happy Harvest / See You Later

episodes.synopsis: Rambunctious young Masha stumbles upon Bear's house in the forest; Masha foils Bear's plans for winter hibernation; Christmas comes to the forest.
episodes.title: How They Met / Don’t Wake Till Spring! / One, Two, Three! Light the Christmas Tree!

episodes.synopsis: Bear and Masha do battle with a jam jar; the wolves' plan to kidnap Masha backfires on them; Masha ruins Bear's attempts to romance a female bear.
episodes.title: Jam Day / Prances with Wolves / Springtime for Bear

episodes.synopsis: Bear teaches Masha how to read tracks; Bear can't remember how he bumped his head; a magical hat grants wishes to Masha and her forest friends.
episodes.title: Tracks of Unknown Animals / Watch Out! / Home Alone

episodes.synopsis: Masha interrupts Bear's peaceful fishing trip; a circus tiger comes to visit his old friend Bear; Masha's constant phone calls wear Bear out.
episodes.title: Gone Fishing! / Stripes and Whiskers / Call Me Please!

episodes.synopsis: Bear tries to take care of rowdy Masha's laundry; Masha and Bear play hide-and-seek; Masha and her friends help Bear repair his home after a mishap.
episodes.title: Laundry Day / Hide and Seek is Not for the Weak / Home Improvement

episodes.synopsis: Masha ropes Bear into teaching her to ice skate; Masha discovers Bear's box of magic tricks; Masha becomes rivals with Bear's little cousin, Panda.
episodes.title: Holiday on Ice / Hocus-Pocus / Little Cousin

episodes.synopsis: Masha cooks up a huge porridge mess; Masha's case of hiccups spreads to all her friends; Bear makes a home for a baby penguin.
episodes.title: Recipe for Disaster / Hold Your Breath! / The Foundling

episodes.synopsis: Masha and Bear play school; after finding a piano in the woods, Bear gives Masha music lessons; Bear asks Masha to keep the hare away from his garden.
episodes.title: First Day of School / The Grand Piano Lesson / No Trespassing!

episodes.synopsis: Masha and her forest friends make a music video; Bear pretends to be sick so Masha will leave him alone; Masha discovers she's a chess prodigy.
episodes.title: One Hit Wonder / Get Well Soon! / Time to Ride My Pony
